2 and N from the largest published GWAS of the trait (e.g., 6.9% and 405,000 for education). Implied SNP-based heritabilities are 15, 16 and 30%, respectively. Parameterizations based on estimates of SNP-based heritabilities (25, 25 and 50%) yield higher projections.

